ing: 1/4 pound American cheese, cut into pieces
1/4 pound provolone cheese, cut into pieces
des: "My family makes this recipe every holiday, it's a favorite that's sure to please. You can serve in with an Italian roll cut into mini pieces served around the dip. enjoy!"
ins: Combine the bologna, ham, salami, pepperoni, American cheese, and provolone cheese in a bowl. Stir in the mayonnaise, garlic powder, and oregano. Sprinkle the pickle, lettuce, and tomato on top.
